'''Molecular properties''' include the [[chemical property|chemical properties]], [[physical property|physical properties]], and [[chemical structure|structural properties]] of [[molecule]]s, including [[drugs]]. Molecular properties typically do not include [[pharmacology|pharmacological]] or [[biological activity|biological]] properties of a [[chemical compound]].
